{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "第七回\"九曲桥上\"——楚留香从金四爷女儿房中出来，发现已被金四爷率领家丁弓箭手包围在九曲桥。金四爷认出楚留香，指责他深夜闯入。楚留香意识到自己陷入了一个圈套，却不知圈套由谁设下。金四爷出手擒拿，以简单却极其有效的武功三次将楚留香摔出，但楚留香以绝顶轻功四次脱身。金四爷转而设酒，暗示让楚留香忘记今夜之事。金四爷道出女儿身患重病、时日无多，恳请楚留香保守秘密。金四爷离去后，白衣女子（金四爷之女）出现，坦言是自己要求楚留香来的——她讨厌所有男人却唯独不讨厌楚留香。她承认自己被人利用作杀楚留香的工具，却不知幕后主使是谁。楚留香怀疑张洁洁，但女子否认认识她。楚留香离去时心中怅然，从墙头跃下却落入一个水盆。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "原来是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我们还真没有想到是你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "我也没想到金四爷居然还认得我。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "像你这样的人，我只要看过一眼，就绝不会忘记。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你有张很特别的脸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "我的脸特别？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "无论谁有你这么样的一张脸，再想规规矩矩的做人都难得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "所以我一眼就看出你绝不是个规规矩矩的人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "所以你才没有忘记我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "但我也没有忘记金四爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "像金四爷这样的人，无论谁看过一眼，都很难忘记的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你既然还认得我，你就不该来。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "只可惜我已经来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你知不知道这里是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你知不知道三十年来，还没有一个人胆敢随意闯入这里！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你怎么到这里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不知道怎么会来？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "就这样糊里糊涂的来了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你连刚才看见的人是谁都不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "不知道，却很想知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她是我的女儿！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你若是看到有人半夜里从你女儿屋里走出来，你会怎么样去对付他？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你真不知道？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "我没有女儿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你知道什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "到现在为止，我只知道一件事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "哪件事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "我只知道我自己好像已掉进个圈套里，忽然间就莫名其妙的掉了下去。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "圈套！什么圈套？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "我若知道这是个什么样的圈套，就不会掉下来了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你是不是还想跳出去？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "想得要命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "一个人若已真的掉在圈套里，就很难再跳出去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "的确很难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你知不知道要怎么样才能出得去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那只有一种法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "请教。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只要你忘记这个圈套，你就已不在这圈套里。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "这句话我不太懂。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你若忘记这是个圈套，哪里还有什么圈套？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "我还是听不懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "要怎样你才懂？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好，我告诉你！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好！好功夫！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "你的功夫也不错。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你再试试这一招！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好，好功夫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "你的功夫也不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "酒来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "请。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "好酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "英雄当饮好酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "昔日青梅煮酒，快论英雄，佳话永传千古，却不知今日之你我，是否能比得上昔日之刘曹？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "比不上。至少我比不上。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "怎见得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "英雄绝不会坐在别人的圈套里走不出去。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "人若还在圈套里，怎能舒舒服服的坐着？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "如此说来，莫非我已走了出去？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那还得看你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你做过父亲没有？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但为人子的，总该明白做父亲并不是件容易事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "的确不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "尤其是做一个垂死女儿的父亲，那更不容易。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你还明白什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "我明白的事本来很多，只可惜有很多却已忘记了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你又是忘记了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "忘记的是那些不该记得的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这件事你也会忘记？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "也许我现在就已忘了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "从此再也不会记起？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "绝不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这话是谁说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "楚留香说的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "请。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "好酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "speaker_name": "金四爷",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "英雄当饮好酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_jin_si_ye",
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "现在你是不是已经完全明白了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你要走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你一定很后悔，根本就不该来的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "但我已经来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你怎么会来的，你自己知不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "不知道也好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你知不知道我以前看过你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "就因为我看过你，所以才要你来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "是你想法子要我来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "别人都说，我这种病只有一种法子能治得好……只有跟男人在一起之后，才能治得好，可是我从来也没有试过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我不信，也不愿意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "不愿意害别人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我并不是个心肠那么好的女人，可是我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "你怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我讨厌男人，一碰到男人就恶心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我要你来，只因为我不讨厌你……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这些话我本不该说出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "你为什么要说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我说出来，只因为我想求你一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不要怪我的父亲，也不要怪别人，因为这件事错的是我，你只能怪我。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "你以为我会怪什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那个要你来的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "你知道她是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我只知道有些人为了十万两银子，连自己兄弟都一样会出卖的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "你不认得张洁洁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "谁是张洁洁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "艾青呢？卜阿鹃呢？你也不认得她们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这些名字我根本从未听说过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "其实你也该怪你自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "因为你也是被人利用的……被利用作杀我的工具！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是谁利用了我？是谁想杀你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "现在我还不知道，但总有一天，我会找到她的！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我只求你一件事，只求你莫要恨我的父亲。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    }
  ],
